                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 12.671,
                                "byte_start": 92088,
                                "byte_stop": 142870,
                                "text": "The judgments and opinion of the court in 79-816, Potomac Electric Power against the Director will be announced by Mr. Justice Stevens.1"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 12.671,
                        "stop": 151.693,
                        "byte_start": 142870,
                        "byte_stop": 698965,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15060,
                            "name": "John Paul Stevens",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/john_paul_stevens",
                            "last_name": "Stevens",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2704,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": 188200800,
                                    "date_end": 1277787600,
                                    "appointing_president": "Gerald Ford",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2704"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32732,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 62101,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/john_paul_stevens.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 12611,
                            "identifier": "john_paul_stevens"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 12.671,
                                "stop": 19.945,
                                "byte_start": 142870,
                                "byte_stop": 171918,
                                "text": "This case comes to us by writ of certiorari from the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 19.945,
                                "stop": 30.194,
                                "byte_start": 171918,
                                "byte_stop": 212878,
                                "text": "It involves the proper measure of compensation for a worker who\u0027s covered by the Longshoremen and Harbor Workers\u0027 Compensation Act."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 30.194,
                                "stop": 39.767,
                                "byte_start": 212878,
                                "byte_stop": 251226,
                                "text": "That Act applies to employers in the District of Columbia by reason of a special act of Congress."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 39.767,
                                "stop": 51.489,
                                "byte_start": 251226,
                                "byte_stop": 298142,
                                "text": "The employee involved in this case suffered a severe injury to his knee which was classified as a permanent partial disability."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 51.489,
                                "stop": 72.258,
                                "byte_start": 298142,
                                "byte_stop": 381211,
                                "text": "The statute contains a schedule of compensation to be awarded for various kinds of physical injuries, one of which is the lost of the use of a leg, and under that schedule this employee is entitled to a specific measured compensation."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 72.258,
                                "stop": 73.576,
                                "byte_start": 381211,
                                "byte_stop": 386436,
                                "text": "His injury is just partial."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 73.576,
                                "stop": 105.015,
                                "byte_start": 386436,
                                "byte_stop": 512241,
                                "text": "He re-continues to work but the -- the statutory scheduled compensation is less than he would receive if he brought -- made his claim under a provision that allows compensation for other cases, cases not specifically listed on the -- on the schedule and he sought recovery as -- and other case which would allow him a substantially larger recovery maybe by a percentage of his lost of earnings and the fixed amount pursuant to the schedule."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 105.015,
                                "stop": 115.378,
                                "byte_start": 512241,
                                "byte_stop": 553619,
                                "text": "The Court of Appeals held that he was entitled to this alternative measure of recovery and the question for us to decide was whether that was a proper reading of the statute."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 115.378,
                                "stop": 131.122,
                                "byte_start": 553619,
                                "byte_stop": 616627,
                                "text": "As we read the statute, the Congress has provided the other cases to cover those which are not on -- on the list and not as an alternative measure of recovery for those for which is a specific recovery is -- is provided."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 131.122,
                                "stop": 148.738,
                                "byte_start": 616627,
                                "byte_stop": 687053,
                                "text": "For that reason, although it may well be true that the statute is in need of reexamination because it\u0027s a rather old schedule, we have decided to reverse the judgment the Court of Appeals and we explained our reasons in some detail in an opinion filed with the clerk today."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 148.738,
                                "stop": 151.693,
                                "byte_start": 687053,
                                "byte_stop": 698965,
                                "text": "Justice Blackman has filed a dissenting opinion."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
